; Regression test for issue #611:
; Verify that journals using the include directive are parsed correctly,
; with all transactions from included files reflected in the balance.
;
; (The original bug was that --trace triggered an assertion failure in
; start_timer() when the included filename caused a description mismatch.
; The fix updated start_timer() to replace the description instead of asserting.)

2024/01/01 Main Payee
    Expenses:Food    $10.00
    Assets:Cash

include 611.dat

2024/02/01 Another Payee
    Expenses:Food    $15.00
    Assets:Cash

test bal
             $-50.00  Assets:Cash
              $50.00  Expenses:Food
--------------------
                   0
end test
